race.comment: CHOCECLAIR (11) kept coming but just failed to pick up the winner over 1100m at this track. Keeps the 2kg claim and maps for the run of the race. Keeps improving and can go one better. RUTHVEN RUSH (2) is third-up and ready to show more like his best. Had no luck at Gatton last time and draws awkwardly again. A live chance if things work out. TOP LEVEL (8) resumes and was last seen 70 days ago placing here fresh for the new yard. She looked promising early doors and has a low gate. The betting should guide to her improvement. Ditto LUCKY JOKER (3) resumes and has been off the scene for a long time. Has the blinkers on does have some ability. CHIDGEY (1) may be next best but would have to find plenty.
